message: “Our goal is to try to recover as many juveniles as possible — to get them out of the life, to try to get them help,” Vilcek said. "... They don’t have many possibilities or places to go outside of that life, and our goal is to set them up through victim witness services to have services provided to them.”

attachments.media_description: FBI, Hagerstown police stage child-trafficking stings on Dual Highway
